quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  39,75,"Ne olilola Abamalaika nibabotokhananga eshisala shioluyali shia Nyasaye, nibatswenulanga Nyasaye wabu Omulesi khutsifumia tsioluyali tsitsie, mana eshina shilibusibwa hakari wabu khubwatoto, ne baliboola mbu: “Okhwitsomibwa khwoosi nikhwa Nyasaye Omulesi webiloonje bioosi."
  40,1,"Ha, Mim."
  40,2,"Okhwishibwa khweshitabu shino khurula khu Nyasaye Owamaani, Omumanyi muno."
  40,3,"Uleshelanga tsimbi khandi ufuchililanga eshileshelo, Oweshinyasio eshilulu, Omuhaani. Abulaho nyasaye tawe halali Ye, ne ewuwe niwo wokhukalukha."
  40,4,"Shibakatsulanga ebimanyisio bia Nyasaye tawe halali balia bakhaya, kho okhuchendana khwabu khushialo khulakhukatia tawe."
  40,5,"Imbeli wabu, Abandu ba Nuhu nende emikanda chindi chiakhaya okhuloonda ka Nyasaye, ne buli omukanda kwali nende amahababa kokhutila Omurumwa wabu, mana nibayingana khubukori khobanyoole okhukalukhania obwatoto, mana nebatiila, kho eshinyasio shianje shiali shirie?"
  40,6,"Ne endi nilwa liakhoyeshela likhuwa lia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi khubakhayi, mbu toto bo ni Abandu bomumulilo."
  40,7,"Ne balia bachinganga eshisala shioluyali shia Nyasaye (Arsh) nende bali mutsimbeka tsiashio bamutswenulanga Nyasaye wabu Omulesi khutsifumia tsitsie tsioluyali, ne bamusuubilanga, ne basabilanga eshileshelo balia basuubila nibaboola mbu: “Nyasaye wefu Omulesi, waswania buli eshindu tsimbabaasi nende obumanyi, kho baleshele balia abasaba eshileshelo mana nibaloonda injila yiyio, ne obekalile eshinyasio shiomulilo."